<C>__{clough}
<D>__{morning lads! lovely yorkshire weather!}
<P>__{(gestures shivering)}
<D>__{i tell you makes me want to jump on a plane right back to majorca!}
<A>__{clough laughs. the players stare in silence. squinting in the drizzle. condensation coming from their mouths. johnny giles stares. billy bremner spits and continues talking disrespectfully.}
